een Doors and Windows Lawn Mowers and Hose Fishing Tackle of all Kind CALL 1611 The CraneKrieg Hardware Co 11 S Park Place A Bailey The Furnace Man Before You Contract for the Heating of that New House liapjpjfam Build Your Own Home Ask for one of our free plan books and let us help you to a home of your own Webb Webb Lumber and Building Supplies Phone 1526 Yards 6th Wilson Phone 1342 ALL OF US want to see good times return when the worker will be em ployed at fair wages the merchant doing business at a reasonable profit and the factories running at maxi mum capacity An all of useveryone of uscan help bring about this condition The first thing to do is to squarely face the facts and above all lets try not to deceive ourselves I All the financial"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:22:41.971Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88078775/1921-03-18/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_lavender_ver01:data:sn88078775:00340580758:1921031801:0511/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=277&w=191", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_lavender_ver01:data:sn88078775:00340580758:1921031801:0511/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=555&w=382", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_lavender_ver01:data:sn88078775:00340580758:1921031801:0511/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1110&w=764", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_lavender_ver01/data/sn88078775/00340580758/1921031801/0511.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["licking", "ohio", "united states", "newark"], "location_city": ["newark"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["licking"], "location_state": ["ohio"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/